        <li><strong>SMS + email order tracking:</strong> auto-sent to customer; reduces your "where's my order?" replies by 80%</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance:</strong> enable for orders > ₹500 (₹3–5 per shipment, covers up to ₹5,000)</li>
