    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 border-b border-ink/10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-ink mb-2">Recommended 3-week sequence</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink/60 mb-6">Some steps unblock others — do them in this order. Designed for evening + weekend work hours.</p>

      <div class="su-week">
        <div class="su-week-label">Week 1</div>
        <div class="su-week-content">
