            <li><strong>Tuesday evening</strong> — Apply for business current account online (HDFC SmartUp or Kotak Neo Biz)</li>
            <li><strong>Wednesday evening</strong> — Search trademark availability (10 min); prepare combined mark image</li>
            <li><strong>Thursday–Saturday</strong> — Bank picks up KYC documents; Shops & Est certificate arrives via email</li>
