    <!-- TIME-SAVING TIPS -->
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 border-b border-ink/10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-ink mb-2">Time-saving tips for an IT day-job + Variolearn evenings</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink/60 mb-6">You're juggling three things. Here are the moves that compress the pickle-business setup to the absolute minimum hours.</p>

      <ol class="su-step-list">
        <li><strong>Apply for everything in parallel where possible.</strong> The above sequence is optimised already — but if something unblocks earlier (e.g., bank account opens in 2 days), pull the next step forward.</li>
        <li><strong>Use Aadhaar e-KYC paths.</strong> GST + FSSAI + Trademark all offer Aadhaar-OTP verification that skips physical document submission. Saves ~5 days per registration.</li>
        <li><strong>Pay 5 years upfront for FSSAI</strong> (₹500 vs ₹100/year). Saves you four renewal cycles. Same logic for trademark renewal at year 10.</li>
        <li><strong>Hire a CA for ~₹3,000 to handle Bookkeeping + ITR filing.</strong> Don't try to file your own ITR-3 with two income sources. Your time is more valuable than ₹3k.</li>
        <li><strong>Pre-printed packing slips + thank-you cards.</strong> Bulk-print 200 of each once. Saves ~30 sec/order on every shipment.</li>
        <li><strong>WhatsApp Business autoresponder</strong> with "We reply by 7 PM daily" — sets customer expectations during your work hours.</li>
        <li><strong>Mom handles all customer service queries during the day.</strong> She has the time + the story. You handle the digital ops at night.</li>
        <li><strong>Batch all shipping for Wed evening + Sat afternoon.</strong> Two packing sessions per week handles ~30–50 orders/month.</li>
        <li><strong>Don't bother with offline retail for the first 6 months.</strong> D2C + Amazon (once State License lands) is enough. Retail visits eat weekends.</li>
        <li><strong>Use Shiprocket Plus (₹999/month) once you cross 100 orders/month.</strong> Gets you 5% off all shipments + priority support — saves more than it costs.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

